OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772041214
OL,3,CReform UK Gorton by-election campaign
OL,4,Cactivist suspended over social media
OL,5,Cposts
OL,7,FA prominent Reform UK figure in the
OL,8,FGorton and Denton by-election campaign
OL,9,Fhas been suspended by the party amid
OL,10,Freports he used racist and misogynist
OL,11,Flanguage on social media.
OL,13,FAdam Mitula, described by Reform
OL,14,FTameside as its interim campaign
OL,15,Fmanager, confirmed he had been
OL,16,Fsuspended by the party pending
OL,17,Finvestigation, but claimed the social
OL,18,Fmedia remarks which led to it were
OL,19,F"taken out of context".
OL,26,@{D@AOU{D@VO]
