OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772041214
OL,3,CReform UK Gorton by-election campaign
OL,4,Cactivist suspended over social media
OL,5,Cposts
OL,7,FSeveral outlets, including the
OL,8,FManchester Mill and Jewish News,
OL,9,Freported that Mr Mitula had been a
OL,10,Fprominent figure in Reform's campaign
OL,11,Fto get Matthew Goodwin elected as the
OL,12,Fnext MP for the Gorton and Denton
OL,13,Fconstituency.
OL,15,FThe media outlets reported Mr Mitula
OL,16,Fhad written posts on social media site
OL,17,FX, formerly Twitter, in which he said
OL,18,Fhe would "never touch a Jewish woman",
OL,19,Fand claimed the Holocaust death toll
OL,20,Fhad been exaggerated.
OL,26,@zD@JOUzD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772041214
OL,3,CReform UK Gorton by-election campaign
OL,4,Cactivist suspended over social media
OL,5,Cposts
OL,7,FHe also reportedly claimed 60% to 70%
OL,8,Fof transgender people are paedophiles.
OL,10,FMr Mitula has since deleted his X
OL,11,Faccount.
OL,13,FHe said: "I'm confirming my suspension
OL,14,Fas a Reform member pending
OL,15,Finvestigation.
OL,17,F"The comments in question were taken
OL,18,Fout of context, and actually defended
OL,19,Fthe Jewish community.
OL,26,@uD@JOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
