PN,39904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772041214
OL,3,CReform UK Gorton by-election campaign
OL,4,Cactivist suspended over social media
OL,5,Cposts
OL,7,F"The original article was published by
OL,8,Fthe Manchester Mill, known for
OL,9,Fspreading misinformation and aligned
OL,10,Fwith political opposition.
OL,12,F"My solicitor is contacting them and
OL,13,Fanyone else spreading false info that
OL,14,Fdamages my reputation."
OL,16,FReform UK said it does not comment on
OL,17,Fits internal disciplinary processes.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUvD@WO]
